Gennady Zyuganov, Leader of the People's Power group Nikolali
Ryzhkov and head of the Agrarian group Nikolai Kharitonov in their
message to the upper house chairman expressed hope that the
Federation Council will invite leaders of parliamentary factions
to its April 22 meeting and listen to a report from the Duma
chairman.
</P>
<P>
