residential, godown and petrol filling station but allowing
development of service apartments. The developer has to complete a
gross floor area of not less than 15,840 square meters on or
before June 30, 2002.
</P>
<P>
The second lot, a relatively remote one located at Sheung Shui,
the "New Territories", was sold for 330 million HK dollars (42.3
million U.S. dollars) while the opening bid was 190 million HK
dollars (24.4 million U.S. dollars). It is also for
non-industrial purposes.
</P>
<P>
This was the first land auction held by the Lands Department
during the 1998-1999 financial year. 
