million shares, infrastructure 522,000 shares, finance 14.236
million shares, hotels 859,000 shares, properties 11.895 million
shares, plantation 4.231 million shares, mining 576,000 shares,
trusts 42,000 shares, closed/fund 184,000 shares and loans 9.883
million shares. 
