Ja'afar who will host a state banquet in honor of the president.
</P>
<P>
On Friday, Compaore is scheduled to attend a briefing at the
Economic Planning Unit in the Prime Minister's Department followed
by a visit to several places, including the Petronas Twin Towers
-- the world's tallest building in the Kuala Lumpur City Center,
and the second national car assembly plant in Rawang near here.
</P>
<P>
On Saturday, he will attend briefings at the Malaysian
Industrial Development Authority and the Malaysian Agricultural
Research and Development Institute on Malaysia's strategies for
investment promotion, economic planning and agro-based production.
</P>
<P>
