<HEADLINE> South China Province Reports Growth in Foreign Trade </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, April 22 (Xinhua) -- Guangdong Province of south
China reported 29.34 billion U.S. dollars in imports and exports
for the first quarter of this year, a rise of 16.2 percent over
the same period last year.
</P>
<P>
