Third-seeded American Jim Courier defeated compatriot Geoff
Grant 6-1, 6-2.
</P>
<P>
Australia's Andrew Ilie beat fourth seed Vincent Spadea of the
United States 6-4, 6-2 and Jan-Michael Gambill ousted sixth seed
Wayne Black of Zimbabwe 7-6 (7-5), 6-2.
</P>
<P>
Last year's runner-up, seventh seed Grant Stafford of South
Africa, advanced by downing Belgium's Johan Van Herck 6-3, 6-1.
</P>
